Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:38.37,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}腾空而起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:43.90,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}定要接近那片光明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.22,0:02:48.02,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}触及希望燎原的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:52.53,op_cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur2}曾经目睹的那个梦想
